      <title>中国谴责美国在电动汽车紧张局势中采取“经典保护主义”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/china-blasts-us-for-classic-protectionism-in-tension-over-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国指责美国采取保护主义贸易措施，有迹象表明华盛顿准备加大力度阻止中国电动汽车进入美国市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/china-blasts-us-for-classic-protectionism-in-tension-over-evs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 16:24:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉提议为巴西优步司机提供更强有力的劳动保护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/brazil-s-lula-to-propose-stronger-labor-protections-for-uber-drivers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦正在推动加强优步科技公司和类似客运应用程序司机的劳工权利，应对困扰世界各地立法者的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/brazil-s-lula-to-propose-stronger-labor-protections-for-uber-drivers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 15:07:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院裁定特朗普可以出现在总统选举中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/supreme-court-rules-trump-can-appear-on-presidential-ballots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院表示，唐纳德·特朗普今年可以参加总统选举，从而结束了全国范围内根据一项很少使用的禁止叛乱分子担任总统的宪法条款禁止他的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/supreme-court-rules-trump-can-appear-on-presidential-ballots</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 15:03:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
